CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 13, 1959, pg. A16, reads: "Junior Aides - A new innovation for D.I.'s was the addition of junior aides as [to] their 'Atlantic City U.S.A.' review Sunday. Above are Paquita Sharp, Dole Ritter, Sylvia Davis, and Juanita Craxter."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Sylvia Davis wearing light colored pants, holding handbag with floral embellishment, standing in front of alternating light colored and dark curtains in Gloria Grate's home in preparation for the D.I.'s "Atlantic City U.S.A." revue held in the Press Room of the Hotel Sherwyn
